Author: Liew Rui Yan <aethernet65535@gmail.com>

mm/damon: add synchronous commit for commit_inputs

This commit modifies the commit_inputs parameter in DAMON LRU_SORT and
RECLAIM to apply parameters synchronously using damon_call(). This allows
parameter validation errors to be returned directly to userspace.

Link: https://lore.kernel.org/20260318153731.97470-1-aethernet65535@gmail.com

